Package com.ibm.as400.vaccess

Class VQueuedMessage

java.lang.Object
com.ibm.as400.vaccess.VQueuedMessage
All Implemented Interfaces:
VObject, Serializable
public class VQueuedMessage extends Object implements VObject, Serializable
Deprecated.
Use Java Swing instead, along with the classes in package com.ibm.as400.access
The VQueuedMessage class defines the representation of a queued message on a system for use in various models and panes in this package.

Most errors are reported as ErrorEvents rather than throwing exceptions. Users should listen for ErrorEvents in order to diagnose and recover from error conditions.

VQueuedMessage objects generate the following events:

  • ErrorEvent
  • VObjectEvent
  • WorkingEvent
